<br>
 To be honest though qaud kiting em by yourself is better exp heh, not as impressive as aoe group though lol. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ulordbug.showPublicProfile?language=EN>LordBug</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_fire.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(4/2/01 8:36:52 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Wyverns of CS strats..</span><hr size=1> BoF seems to work fine against them.  Quad-kiting them can be done, but be ready to get flamed by everyone else in the zone.  Of course, you need to avoid the drakes when doing this too. <p><BR><BR>
